<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:08:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>艾米·舒默因在加沙战争中为以色列而战而受到批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amy-schumer-draws-fire-for-coming-out-fighting-for-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018b-b43f-df42-a78f-bd7f0b260000</link><description>自10月7日以来，这位犹太喜剧演员一直是以色列在好莱坞最强有力的倡导者。然而，她的社交媒体帖子让她被指控“仇恨巴勒斯坦人和穆斯林”以及“盗用”马丁·路德·金。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 15:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amy-schumer-draws-fire-for-coming-out-fighting-for-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018b-b43f-df42-a78f-bd7f0b260000</guid></item><item><title>越来越多的以色列士兵正在记录并公布他们自己对巴勒斯坦人的虐待行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/growing-number-of-idf-soldiers-are-documenting-and-posting-their-own-abuse-of-palestinians/0000018b-ae60-dea2-a9bf-fefe96070000</link><description>在社交媒体视频中，以色列士兵殴打和羞辱巴勒斯坦被拘留者，其中一些人在受到虐待后不久就被释放。以色列国防军则对部分案件的肇事者进行了惩罚，称这种行为违反了军队价值观</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 15:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/growing-number-of-idf-soldiers-are-documenting-and-posting-their-own-abuse-of-palestinians/0000018b-ae60-dea2-a9bf-fefe96070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女子涉嫌在MK家附近喷漆“1,400”，警方询问她投票给谁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-spraying-1-400-near-home-of-mk-asked-by-police-who-she-voted-for/0000018b-b40c-d3c1-a39b-beed5ffa0000</link><description>在审讯中，以色列警方询问嫌疑人耶尔·阿巴迪·赖斯 (Yael Abadi Reiss)，她在 10 月 7 日做了什么，以及她是否投票给以色列现任政府。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-spraying-1-400-near-home-of-mk-asked-by-police-who-she-voted-for/0000018b-b40c-d3c1-a39b-beed5ffa0000</guid></item><item><title>“使用武力永远不会有助于和平”：亚美尼亚总统会谈纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫、伊朗和以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-force-will-never-contribute-to-peace-an-interview-with-armenias-president/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff0a310000</link><description>亚美尼亚总统瓦哈格恩·哈恰图良（Vahagn Khachaturyan）的同胞因阿塞拜疆的闪电袭击而逃离纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫，几周后他希望两国之间实现持久和平。他还渴望与以色列建立更好的关系：“我们作为国家非常相似。我们俩都在种族灭绝中幸存下来。我们知道这意味着什么&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-force-will-never-contribute-to-peace-an-interview-with-armenias-president/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff0a310000</guid></item><item><title>据报道以色列袭击后大马士革国际机场关闭一个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/damascus-intl-airport-shut-for-a-month-following-reported-israeli-strikes/0000018b-b3e9-df42-a78f-bfebf9590000</link><description>这是自罢工开始以来该设施停运时间最长的一次。叙利亚和伊朗航空公司现在飞往俄罗斯空军部署地拉塔基亚</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/damascus-intl-airport-shut-for-a-month-following-reported-israeli-strikes/0000018b-b3e9-df42-a78f-bfebf9590000</guid></item><item><title>支持和反以色列的示威者在洛杉矶放映哈马斯暴行镜头外发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</link><description>在宽容博物馆举行的放映是众多私人放映之一，旨在让舆论制造者了解哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列边境社区的残酷程度</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</guid></item><item><title>一个更加军事化的以色列将是一个不那么繁荣的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</link><description>加沙战争大规模调动储备金对经济产生了深远影响。战后以色列将需要他们继续服役</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</guid></item><item><title>新闻机构对以色列关于哈马斯大屠杀共谋的指控提出异议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</link><description>亲以色列媒体监管机构的报告很快被以色列外交部采纳，声称新闻媒体“在 10 月 7 日大屠杀期间让记者与哈马斯恐怖分子混在一起”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人厌恶内塔尼亚胡。但对与巴勒斯坦人实现和平的绝望感更深</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</link><description>随着内塔尼亚胡的支持率跌至历史低点，10月7日哈马斯袭击后的以色列民意调查显示，战后结束血腥的巴以冲突的希望更加黯淡</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:44:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方解雇了拒绝与本·格维尔一起参加活动的安全志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</link><description>这位志愿者向《国土报》解释说：“我不会在拍完照片后就看到自己出现在本-格维尔的竞选活动中。”据他透露，警方一开始声称只有在与部长一起的仪式上才能向他发放枪支</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</guid></item><item><title>德国人纪念水晶之夜，反犹太主义再次抬头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article/germans-commemorate-kristallnacht-as-antisemitism-is-on-the-rise-again/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff79890000</link><description>柏林犹太社区卡哈尔·阿达斯·吉斯罗尔 (Kahal Adass Jisroel) 的经理上个月在犹太教堂遭到燃烧弹袭击时遭到袭击，他表示，德国在保护犹太人方面做得还不够。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article/germans-commemorate-kristallnacht-as-antisemitism-is-on-the-rise-again/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff79890000</guid></item><item><title>四名前阿拉伯裔以色列议员因反战抗议计划被警方拘留质询</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/four-former-arab-israeli-lawmakers-detained-for-questioning-over-plans-for-antiwar-protest/0000018b-b3b5-dedf-adab-f7b5c11e0000</link><description>阿拉伯高级监督委员会主席、前以色列议会成员穆罕默德·巴拉克首先受到讯问，随后三名前巴拉德党议员和总干事也受到讯问，罪名是涉嫌组织“可能导致煽动或损害公共和平”的集会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/four-former-arab-israeli-lawmakers-detained-for-questioning-over-plans-for-antiwar-protest/0000018b-b3b5-dedf-adab-f7b5c11e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯认为什么是加沙的“胜利”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/what-would-israel-and-hamas-consider-a-win-in-gaza/0000018b-b365-dedf-adab-f7755a140000</link><description>对于以色列来说，此时此地消灭恐怖组织将被视为胜利。哈马斯希望维持永久的冲突状态，因此只要活着再战斗就将被其领导人视为胜利</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:25:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/what-would-israel-and-hamas-consider-a-win-in-gaza/0000018b-b365-dedf-adab-f7755a140000</guid></item><item><title>“完成工作”：在共和党总统辩论中，候选人竞相支持以色列对哈马斯的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/at-gop-presidential-debate-candidates-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-the-job/0000018b-b1f3-df42-a78f-bdf3fb760000</link><description>在共和党犹太联盟共同主办的辩论中，蒂姆·斯科特指责拜登双手沾满鲜血 ■ 罗恩·德桑蒂斯嘲笑“伊斯兰恐惧症” ■ 孤立主义者维韦克·拉马斯瓦米称乌克兰泽连斯基为“纳粹”，尼基·黑利为“穿高跟鞋的迪克·切尼”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/at-gop-presidential-debate-candidates-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-the-job/0000018b-b1f3-df42-a78f-bdf3fb760000</guid></item><item><title>“我们 24/7 全天候运营”：保存以色列士兵精子的竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-operate-24-7-the-race-to-preserve-israeli-soldiers-sperm/0000018b-af34-dea2-a9bf-ffbee1470000</link><description>在以色列与加沙哈马斯的战斗中，当局加大了对阵亡士兵精子利用的力度，并将道德问题留待以后处理。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:13:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-operate-24-7-the-race-to-preserve-israeli-soldiers-sperm/0000018b-af34-dea2-a9bf-ffbee1470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队白天对约旦河西岸发动空袭，造成至少 10 名巴勒斯坦人死亡、20 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-conduct-daytime-airstrike-in-west-bank-at-least-seven-palestinians-killed/0000018b-b397-dea2-a9bf-f39f87b80000</link><description>拉马拉巴勒斯坦卫生部报告称，共有八名巴勒斯坦人在西岸冲突和罢工中丧生；七个在杰宁难民营，两个在希伯伦和伯利恒附近</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 11:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-conduct-daytime-airstrike-in-west-bank-at-least-seven-palestinians-killed/0000018b-b397-dea2-a9bf-f39f87b80000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级将领警告以色列长期加沙战争的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/top-u-s-general-cautions-over-risks-in-a-long-gaza-war/0000018b-b398-df42-a78f-bfdb90eb0000</link><description>参谋长联席会议主席查尔斯·Q·布朗将军表示，以色列在加沙的军事行动的既定目标是彻底摧毁哈马斯，这是“一项相当大的命令”。他还表示，以色列国防军对其行为的公开解释还有改进的空间</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 10:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/top-u-s-general-cautions-over-risks-in-a-long-gaza-war/0000018b-b398-df42-a78f-bfdb90eb0000</guid></item><item><title>西方和阿拉伯官员齐聚巴黎讨论加沙援助；马克龙推动人道主义停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/western-arab-officials-talk-gaza-aid-in-paris-macron-pushes-for-humanitarian-ceasefire/0000018b-b343-d3c1-a39b-bfe370e30000</link><description>据估计，超过 150 万人（约占加沙人口的 70%）逃离家园，应对巴勒斯坦地区的危机大约需要 12 亿美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 10:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/western-arab-officials-talk-gaza-aid-in-paris-macron-pushes-for-humanitarian-ceasefire/0000018b-b343-d3c1-a39b-bfe370e30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谴责定居者的暴力行为，以此向拜登示好，然后急忙安抚他的支持者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-condemns-settler-violence-as-a-gesture-to-biden-then-rushes-to-appease-his-base/0000018b-b32a-dedf-adab-f73a764b0000</link><description>就在内塔尼亚胡在拜登的推动下谴责定居者的暴力行为几个小时后，他声称暴力行为来自定居点以外的“极少数”。拜登面临内部批评越来越多，美国加大对以色列施压，要求停火</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 09:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-condemns-settler-violence-as-a-gesture-to-biden-then-rushes-to-appease-his-base/0000018b-b32a-dedf-adab-f73a764b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的 TROPHY 系统如何保护部队免受加沙反坦克导弹的攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-trophy-system-anti-tank-missiles-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</link><description>哈马斯发布了许多视频，显示其部队向以色列军队发射反坦克导弹。在大多数情况下，它们实际上展示了以色列先进的拦截技术正在发挥作用</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-trophy-system-anti-tank-missiles-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</guid></item></channel></rss>